<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q28_v12" title="Q28_v12" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Para purificar el agua en una planta de tratamiento, se utiliza un sistema de filtrado automático.</p>
    <p>La rapidez de filtrado <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:math>, medida en litros por hora (L/h), se puede modelar con la expresión 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>r</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mi>V</m:mi>
          <m:mi>t</m:mi>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>,
      donde <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi></m:math> es el volumen total de agua filtrada, en litros, y <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> es el tiempo, en horas, que tarda el sistema en filtrar todo ese volumen.</p>
    <p>Si se necesita filtrar 900 L de agua en 45 minutos, ¿con qué rapidez, en L/h, debe trabajar el sistema para lograrlo?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">20 L/h<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mi>min</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mi>h</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mi>h</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, la rapidez necesaria es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> L/h. Si el sistema trabajara a 20 L/h durante <m:math><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:math> h, filtraría solo <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> L, que no son 900 L.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">1200 L/h<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Primero, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mi>min</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mi>h</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mi>h</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>. Luego, usando <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> L/h. Por lo tanto, esa es la rapidez necesaria.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">120 L/h<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mi>min</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mi>h</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, la rapidez necesaria es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> L/h. Si el sistema trabajara a 120 L/h durante <m:math><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:math> h, filtraría solo <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>120</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> L, que no son 900 L.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">675 L/h<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mi>min</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mi>h</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, la rapidez necesaria es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> L/h. Si el sistema trabajara a 675 L/h durante <m:math><m:mn>0,75</m:mn></m:math> h, filtraría <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>675</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,75</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>506,25</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> L, que no son 900 L.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar los datos</strong></p>
            <p>El volumen total es 900 L y el tiempo es 45 minutos.</p>
            <p>La fórmula dada es:
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>r</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                    <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Convertir el tiempo a horas</strong></p>
            <p>Como la rapidez se pide en L/h, el tiempo debe expresarse en horas.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>45</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>min</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>45</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>60</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mi>h</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mi>h</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>0,75</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>h</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reemplazar en la fórmula</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>r</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mi>V</m:mi>
                    <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>900</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>0,75</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Calcular la rapidez</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>900</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>0,75</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>1200</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, la rapidez necesaria es 1200 L/h.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la B: 1200 L/h.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>